</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><div class="language-typescript ext-ts line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-typescript"><code><span class="token comment">// android 通过重写事件控制</span>
